This is the terrifying moment a female lion tamer was mauled by one of her animals in a circus in Egypt - ten years after her husband was killed performing the same act.

Faten El-Helw is seen prancing around the ring and waving to her adoring fans when the big cat suddenly leaps from its stool and lunges at her.

As the panicked audience jump to their feet  screaming, the lion tamer is pinned to the ground and bitten in the shoulder.

